p.d: The companion of an important winegrower dies after falling out of a window. Four years ago his first wife had committed suicide in exactly the same spot. Coincidence? At the time, Déa was in charge of the investigation... Directed by: Akim Isker (France, 2019) Screenplay: Camille Pouzol, Maxime Crupaux Cast: Carole Weyers (Déa Versini), François Vincentelli (Jimmy), Ambroise Michel (Matthieu Delcourt), Bruno Gouery (Fred Jolin), Fleur Geffrier (Jeanne Granger), Pierre Laplace (Xavier Fremont), Bastien Bernini (Damien), Benjamin Bellecour (Vincent), Tom Novembre (André de Brunetier) Genre: detective Awards: best actress (Carole Weyers), 2019 Séries Mania festival
